    <anchor n="T.50.2061.0797c12"/><head><date from-iso="0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="0907-06-06">唐</date>杭州天竺山靈隱寺<persName key="A010894">守直</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0797c13"/><persName key="A010894">釋守直</persName>，字<persName key="A010894">堅道</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000011520">錢塘</placeName>人也，姓范氏，齊<placeName key="PL000000013662">信安</placeName>太<lb
ed="T" n="0797c14"/>守<persName key="A010895">瑝</persName>之八葉。禮既冠眾，君子器之。夙有丘<lb
ed="T" n="0797c15"/>園之期，不顧玄纁之錫。遂詣蘇州<placeName key="PL000000010025">支硎寺</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0797c16"/><persName key="A010896">圓大師</persName>所受具足律儀。是夜，眼中光現長一<lb
ed="T" n="0797c17"/>丈餘，持久方滅，蓋得戒之驗也。後抵<placeName key="PL000000027764">江陵</placeName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0797c18"/>依<persName key="A010425">真公</persName>。三年練行。尋禮天下二百餘郡，聖<lb
ed="T" n="0797c19"/>跡所至，無不至焉。見<persName key="A001342">無畏三藏</persName>，為受菩薩<lb
ed="T" n="0797c20"/>戒。聞<persName key="A009319">普寂大師</persName>傳《楞伽》心印。講《起信》宗論<lb
ed="T" n="0797c21"/>二十餘遍；<persName key="A001519">南山</persName>律鈔<ptr target="#n1290"/>四十遍，平等一雨，大小<lb
ed="T" n="0797c22"/>雙機在乎圓音，未嘗少異。乃立願誦《華嚴<lb
ed="T" n="0797c23"/>經》，還於中宵夢神人施珠一顆。及覺，惘惘<lb
ed="T" n="0797c24"/>然如珠在握。是歲入<placeName key="PL000000005250">五臺山</placeName>，轉《華嚴經》二<lb
ed="T" n="0797c25"/>百遍，追夙心也。宏覽《大藏經》三過，廣正<lb
ed="T" n="0797c26"/>見也。至<date from-iso="0738-01-29" key="j19906371991020" to-iso="0739-02-16">開元二十六年</date>，有制舉高行，俗道<lb
ed="T" n="0797c27"/>請正名隷大林寺<!--找不到此地-->，後移籍天竺住<placeName key="PL000000011567">靈隱峯</placeName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0797c28"/>時<date from-iso="0767-02-08" key="j20012392001592" to-iso="0768-01-27">大曆二年</date>也。至<date from-iso="0770-04-05" key="j20023912002419" to-iso="0770-05-03">五年三月</date>，寓于龍興淨土<lb
ed="T" n="0797c29"/>院<!--找不到此地-->，謂左右曰：「夫至人乘如而來，乘如而去，<pb ed="T" n="0798a" xml:id="T50.2061.0798a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0798a01"/>示其心然也。而愚夫欲以長繩繫彼白日，<lb
ed="T" n="0798a02"/>安可得乎？<persName key="A010894">吾</persName>景落桑榆，豈淹久也？」以其年<lb
ed="T" n="0798a03"/><date key="j20024192002419" when-iso="0770-05-03">此月二十九日</date>告終，春秋七十一，僧臘四十<lb
ed="T" n="0798a04"/>五。其間臨壇度人多矣，顯名者<placeName key="PL000000010052">洞庭</placeName><persName key="A010899">辯秀</persName>、<lb
ed="T" n="0798a05"/><placeName key="PL000000013012">湖州</placeName><persName key="A008833">皎然</persName>、<persName key="A010900">惠普</persName>、<persName key="A010901">道莊</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000013240">會稽</placeName><persName key="A010902">清江</persName>、<persName key="A010904">清源</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000011519">杭州</placeName><persName key="A010905">擇隣</persName>、<lb
ed="T" n="0798a06"/><persName key="A010906">神偃</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000009739">常州</placeName><persName key="A010907">道進</persName>。<persName key="A008833">晝公</persName>著《塔銘》云。</p>
